title: O'NEILL PSYCHOFREAK 2013/14
description: The 2013 O'Neill Psychofreak features O'Neill's exclusive TechnoButter Air technology, which is lighter, more insulating and quick drying than ever. With state-of-the-art insulation in the chest, back and in the lower core panels. The all-new TechnoButter in the arms, shoulders and lower leg add flex and durability to the right places. Psychofreak takes you beyond warm, beyond flexible and beyond your imagination and will make you "Surf Lighter, Surf Longer". TechnoButter Neoprene is the most advanced super stretch neoprene available on the market: 20% lighter, 30% less water absorption with quick dry properties. SuperSeam Weld, which is 60% Thinner and Lighter than all other fluid seam welds. The Psychofreak also features Z.E.N. Zip Closure System. It's floating zipper design makes this closure the highest performance on the market.
